flowchart LR
    %% Actors
    User([👤 Customer])
    Sys([⚙️ Subsystem: RAG Orchestrator])
    VDB[(🗄️ Vector Database)]
    LLM[(🧠 OpenAI API)]
    HeyGen([🎥 HeyGen API])

    %% User Actions
    User -->|1| AskQ(Ask Support Question)
    User -->|6| Watch(View Avatar & Read Sources)

    %% System Use Cases
    subgraph Use Cases - Project Vanguard
        AskQ -.->|<< include >> \n 2| Ext(Extract Context)
        AskQ -.->|<< include >> \n 3| Eval(Evaluate Confidence Threshold)
        
        Eval -.->|If Score < X \n 4a| Decline(Decline Answer Gracefully)
        Eval -.->|If Score >= X \n 4b| Gen(Generate AI Response)
        
        Gen -.->|<< include >> \n 5| AV(Fetch Avatar Video)
    end

    %% Backend Dependencies
    Ext --> VDB
    Gen --> LLM
    AV --> HeyGen
    
    %% Output
    Decline --> Watch
    Gen --> Watch
